scene.message:
Reiji: You really won't{nl}
let us through?{wait_fr:86}{nl}
...You'll die.{waitkey}{ret}

Man in Black: Don't make{nl}
me say it again.{nl}
Beyond here is under{nl}
SEBEC control.{waitkey}{nl}
Resist, and you'll{nl}
be shot.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That idiot!{nl}
He's gonna get{nl}
himself killed!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh heh, sorry 'bout{nl}
him — he's a little off.{nl}
C'mon, move it, blockhead.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Oh?...{nl}
Even you help people?{nl}
Now that truly is{nl}
a bolt from the blue.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Idiot.{nl}
Even a guy like that's got{nl}
a mom who'd cry{nl}
if he died.{waitkey}{ret}

Man in Black: You cannot{nl}
pass this point.{nl}
This area is{nl}
off-limits.{waitkey}{ret}

Man in Black: This is no{nl}
place for children.{nl}
Get somewhere safe.{nl}
Now.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sheesh, that guy...{nl}
What the heck is{nl}
going on?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: SEBEC...{nl}
What are you plotting,{nl}
Kandori?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Doesn't sit right...{nl}
So they're more than{nl}
just a company, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What on earth?{nl}
I had heard SEBEC was{nl}
a first-rate company...{waitkey}{nl}
They're no different{nl}
from the Mafia.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh?{nl}
Isn't that the{nl}
transfer student?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Huh?{nl}
Wait, that's Kido!{nl}
What's he doing{nl}
out here?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kido Reiji.{nl}
A student who transferred{nl}
here six months ago.{nl}
Quiet; always acts alone.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Man in Black: Who are you?{nl}
Beyond this point is{nl}
under SEBEC control.{nl}
Entry is prohibited.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey — SEBEC.{nl}
That's Maki's mom's{nl}
company, right?{nl}
What the heck's going on?{waitkey}{ret}
